Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-----TXT-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.58,0:00:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腦袋…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腦袋要裂開了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道這是黑暗同盟的新一輪攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都跟你說了不要點中份的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把品嘗一半的權利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賜給你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就這樣開始了兩個人的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.85,0:00:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我和六花  值得珍惜的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  怎麼沒有牽著狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30}西鄉隆盛，日本幕末政治家，生於鹿兒島。其右手牽犬的塑像非常有名。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿兒島上的西鄉公像都是不帶狗的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊  這可是西鄉公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一提到他不就應該牽著狗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然搞不太清楚  我們還是去看別的西鄉公像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那裡竟然有狗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗在那裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來  茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和小組走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裡走散的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在土產店…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}要不給他們打個電話？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}啊  還有這招！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼啦  好不容易考完放假了一大早就來電話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽到我的留言了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,區區冒牌魔術師不要隨便用我的語音信箱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少廢話  快點把那些都刪除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刪除？把你的存在刪除嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦  我說的是那個網頁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:03:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是你擅自做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢  莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是因為最近胖了就拿我來撒氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞎說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別想蒙混過去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了  在我回來之前沒刪除掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等著被我灌上五升牛奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個冒牌貨  好不容易打電話給我淨說些奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為她會說  分別了幾天想聽凸守的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者問問我過得好不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說是什麼網頁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡看還真是壯觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到這麼雄偉的火山就在我們身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感應到了方圓5公里以內的共振
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠近火山口處傳來魔族的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說是  紅龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧你能編出這麼一大堆設定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太  莫非紅龍的本體已在火山口解體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分散成了七個部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有必要把它們全都收集…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:03:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  你想到對岸去看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去對岸？我們能過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  看起來可以坐船過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去對岸…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Schwarz  Schnee  Scraper
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漆黑冰雪突刺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Schnee  Gretchen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寒冰結界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你幻想的東西應該一個都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正還有時間  不用太…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是勇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我沒想到會在這裡碰到勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.00,0:04:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的臺詞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你也是來修學旅行的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是曾經和我生死與共的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪王真眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才因為太激動了才跟他抱在一起  我道歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法魔王少女  蘇菲婭寧·SP·薩圖恩七世
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你踏入了我的邪王黑暗結界的中心領域
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想開戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非你們倆一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人獨處啊  那今天就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘇菲婭寧還背負著搜尋天使的使命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我往那邊  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  能不能借我500元錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復活啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你會把包丟在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是天使幹的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且零之地帶對南部地區的影響也很大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己回得了旅館嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:06:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心  路我都記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少騙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看出來了  其實你根本不知道怎麼回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手機也在包裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.46,0:06:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正世間萬物都是相連的  條條大路通羅馬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我肯定能回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了你  我不會再接近其他女生了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個給你  想去哪裡就去哪裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別想用錢了事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  六花？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用邪王真眼的力量很快就能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟著我  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來包裡有張紙條來著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:06:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}（森大人的私語）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這冒牌大人憑什麼冒充森大人的名號啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼  那不是你自己做的網站嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凸守才不知道有這個網站
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是你這個冒牌貨做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？你覺得可能嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是誰幹的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你問我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說  是本尊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還來這裡轉過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這裡有天使的反應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你記不記得什麼時候打開過包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和朋友上車下車
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,買了零食之後分別了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後一邊吃一邊在這附近轉悠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說  買東西的時候包還在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖精之樹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去有很高的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還真是在奇怪的地方意趣相投
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是啊  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪王真眼  有兩下子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憑藉邪王真眼之力  當然不在話下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天使！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  是猴子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗耳目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了是猴子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憑藉我的邪王真眼之力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,區區一兩頭猿人  輕鬆送上西天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別鬧了  小心被咬到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想辦法趕走它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話說不定會追過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮  你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那之陣·改
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  勇者！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用這招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花退後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那之陣·改！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了  勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:09:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那之陣·改  久違地又一次成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過沒想到你還真記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下定決心了  永遠不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論是那時和勇者一同養成的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是身為魔法魔王少女所背負的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宮也是個怪傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不奇怪  只是不想改變
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼  遊戲幣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的記憶果然已經被奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太  勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來  站得起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了  勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  六花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:11:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太你…已經把契約給忘了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六花？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  六花！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪王真眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這座西鄉公像也不牽狗的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿兒島上的西鄉公像是不帶狗的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是小鳥游同學吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望她別迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電話也不接
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  這次全都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易你們倆單獨出來玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一心想要搶回包  沒有顧及六花的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以七宮你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的修學旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  剛好那邊有公交站
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要回到車站就知道路了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你該減減肥了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好  這裡是富樫家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是七宮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智音姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然打擾很抱歉  但我有些事情想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是七宮跟富樫君在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說把小鳥游同學晾在一邊  他們倆玩去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是小鳥游同學不是變成一個人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為我離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  富樫君做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:37.17,post,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz17.71\pos(1162,212)}收件箱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:37.17,post,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz17.71\pos(1182,336)}我是蘇菲婭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有地圖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你見到六花了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富樫君你做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人在一起的時候還顧著七宮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她當然會生氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是啊  你知道她去哪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了地圖之後就跑開了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊  總之我來搞定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樟葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  你做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  把你叫到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧  我一個人來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有人來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醜話說在前頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪王真眼是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論你使用任何居於最高位的光明魔法也無法戰勝我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要住手的話就趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我在這個世界現身的肉體反應速度極快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是無法…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看破的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你就親身體驗一下魔法魔王少女的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然想這麼說來著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是讓你來這裡不是跟你戰鬥的  是有些事想告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想著你是不是誤會了我跟勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是勇者是勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直叫他勇者  勇者就是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點就讓著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者跟邪王真眼締結了戀人的契約對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:16:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到勇者就心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要跟他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這樣一來很多事情都變了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有錯  魔族反應很明顯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  蘇菲婭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是其他世界線的異次元現身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會漸漸失去力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺自己不再是魔法魔王少女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺這種事情已經無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要一直這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要根據世界真理和連關天則
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為魔法魔王少女  做好我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是魔法魔王少女  蘇菲婭寧·SP·薩圖恩七世
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捨棄一切  與此力量一同  終我此生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以勇者的搭檔是邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你準備一直做邪王真眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要喚醒暗炎龍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要把那個遊戲幣…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個本來就是我拿著的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是勇者好像已經不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說笑呢  這話不該我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有天使的反應了  那麼我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再會！
