Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒牌貨快點坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Mabinogion
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個問題涉及到黑暗聖典中最複雜的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是真貨  肯定能答得上來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.39,0:19:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘇菲婭都告訴我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該道歉的應該是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於一同浴血奮戰至今的漆黑烈焰使的懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓我無比悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是事實上我倆也沒怎麼能在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然說到現在才說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該說都已經這時候了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者說時機非常不湊巧該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不是今天就沒有意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是你生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為很可能被讀取思考
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個情報應該屬於最重要的機密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前的郵箱名上寫的清清楚楚好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前那把有點破了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.56,0:20:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得你收到這個會很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Schwarzschild
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漆黑傘盾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(640,656)}Schwarzschild
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漆黑傘盾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在前天去的地方做的  附贈的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…難道是黑暗力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你準備一直做邪王真眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要喚醒暗炎龍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,0:21:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太你認為暗炎龍在你體內嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天會變身為GelZone  UNSAS嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  暗炎龍先不說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定體內真的沉睡著什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我覺得什麼都沒有才是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是覺得有什麼在體內也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說如此  漆黑烈焰還是放不出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在已經放出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡你
